PRIVACY POLICY
Simka built the Bedtime story app as a Freemium app. This SERVICE is provided by Simka at no cost and is intended for use as is.
This page is used to inform visitors regarding my policies with the collection, use, and disclosure of Personal Information if anyone decided to use my Service.
If you choose to use my Service, then you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. The Personal Information that I collect is used for providing and improving the Service. I will not use or share your information with anyone except as described in this Privacy Policy.
​
​
INFO
RMATION COLLECTION
When using our application, we collect certain information:
Your User ID: It is necessary for you to use certain features of our application.
Purchase History: We use your purchase history to understand your preferences and improve our services.
Crash Logs and Diagnostics: We collect this information to enhance the stability and performance of our application.
Device ID: This allows us to understand how many unique users use our application and detect any suspicious or fraudulent activity.
Additionally, we utilize OpenAI's API for chat functionalities and Qonversion SDK for in-app purchase management.
Ple
ase see ChatGPT's & Qonversion privacy policy for more information on how this data is used.
NFORMATION USE
We use your information for the purpose of providing, improving, personalizing, and developing our application. More specifically, we use your information to:
Provide you with services you have requested.
Enhance the application based on user feedback and crash diagnostics.
Customize your user experience based on your preferences and purchase history.
Safeguard our application against fraudulent or illegal activities.
Communicate with you regarding application updates, changes in our services or our Privacy Policy.
​
​
INFORMATION SHARING
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share your personal information with third parties only under the following circumstances:
Service Providers: We may share your information with third parties that provide services on our behalf such as data analysis, customer support, and security management. This includes OpenAI, which provides the ChatGPT API, and Qonversion, which provides the SDK for in-app purchases.
Legal Obligations: We may disclose your information if we are required to do so by
law or if we believe in good faith that it is necessary to comply with a legal obligation
